= //(Written by [[user OriTiefling]] and drawn by [[user winkwonkboi]].)//
@@ @@
[[div class="blockquote"]]
[[=]]
**__Artist's Commentary__**

Okay, where the fuck did I get this motivation to draw?

You know, I thought I'd just focus on finishing up my post for GoblinCon, but one thing led to another, and now I'm here writing the commentary for another piece of art I drew in a few hours.

Someone please look into this. I think an anomaly has breached into my headspace and it keeps convincing me to continuously draw and draw and draw and post (I am joking, of course. Anyways, yeah, that's all from me. Maybe the next time you see me is on another artwork page, lol. Although, I doubt I have the energy to at this point.

Peace. ✌️
[[/=]]
